seller.oneLinerTitle: Let's create an amazing video together!
seller.description:
Greetings, 
I'm a creative professional Video Editor and VFX Artist. 
I've successfully finished projects for short films, TV, music videos, social media and more. 
I provide services for post video processing such as: 
Video editing 
Visual effects 
Color correction Keying (removing the green or blue screen) 
Rotoscoping 
Clean up objects, logos/brands 
Retouch and beauty work for actors/models. 

If you can, please take a moment to check out my portfolio, video reel, and client feedback! 
Feel free to get in touch with me if you have any questions. 
Thank you for your time,

Sanjay Been

reviews.comment: It's always a joy to work with Sanjay. He always works very hard to give us everything we hope to get. I will return again and again for his help. :)
Sanjay has always been very careful to do everything he can to get all the detail correct. It a joy to work with him.
Great job from Sanjay again, he is my go-to guy.
